Mineral Resources are not Mineral Reserves
and do not have demonstrated economic viability. There is no certainty that any part of the Mineral Resources estimated will be
converted into a Mineral Reserves estimate;

Quantity and grade of reported Inferred
resources are uncertain in nature and there has been insufficient exploration to classify these Inferred resources as Measured
or Indicated;

Mineral Resources and Reserves were estimated
using the guidelines set out in the CIM Definition Standards for Mineral Resources and Reserves prepared by the CIM Standing Committee
on Reserve Definitions, reserves estimates are also compliant with SEC Industry Guide 7;
